Subject: [PATCH] Initial scaffold: React + TypeScript + Vite portfolio with
 routing, styles, and GSAP setup

### Motivation

- Provide an initial application skeleton for the Kylie Bi portfolio using React, TypeScript, and Vite so visual refinement and content can be added on a solid foundation.

### Description

- Add project configuration and build files including `package.json`, `vite.config.ts`, and TypeScript configs (`tsconfig.json`, `tsconfig.app.json`, `tsconfig.node.json`).
- Create app entry and routing with `index.html`, `src/main.tsx`, `src/router.tsx`, a `Layout` component in `src/components/Layout`, and `Home`/`NotFound` pages under `src/pages`.
- Add styling setup with `src/styles/global.css` and CSS Modules for `Layout` and `Home` components, and include a minimal `src/vite-env.d.ts`.
- Prepare third-party animation support by registering `ScrollTrigger` in `src/lib/gsap.ts` and add documentation files `README.md`, `docs/project-structure.md`, and `AGENTS.md` describing project rules and commands.

### Testing

- No automated tests are configured for this repository yet.
